<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Feb1931"><font color="red">4 February 1931</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to T.S. Eliot): He has been lately nervously exhausted on account &hellip; Sullivan &hellip; He is working at Part II but his eyes are still a great hindrance. Moreover the recent marriage of his son and the fact that he is changing his apartment have taken up a lot of his time. </div>
